 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Recommends:
 hip-dev,
 hsa-rocr-dev,
 hsakmt-roct-dev,
 libdrm-dev,
 rocm-xio-bnxt-re-dkms,
 rocm-xio-ernic-eth-rdma-dkms,
 rocm-xio-ionic-eth-rdma-dkms,
Description: ROCm GPU-Initiated IO library
 Static library, headers, CMake package config, bundled
 patched rdma-core (v62.0 with vendor DV support), udev
 rules, and DKMS kernel module for rocm-xio.
 .
 rocm-xio enables GPU-initiated IO operations including
 RDMA, NVMe, and SDMA endpoint access from AMD GPUs.

Package: xio-tester
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 rocm-xio (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: rocm-xio test and benchmarking tool
 Command-line tool for testing and benchmarking
 rocm-xio endpoints (RDMA, NVMe, SDMA, test-ep).
 .
 Depends on the rocm-xio package for udev rules, the
 DKMS kernel module, and bundled rdma-core libraries.
